text: Khalikeyevo () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Khalikeyevsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 350 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 9 km from Sterlibashevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Khalikeyevo
